snippet.title: Medal of Honor Heroes 2 Multiplayer Trailer
snippet.description: Check out this video which highlights 32-person online multiplayer game on Wii and PSP!  Fight against anyone and anytime.  Coming shipping November 13, 2007 on Wii and PSP. Check out mohheroes2.ea.com for more info.
